---
// Plain-SVG diagram for the local-first data flow as of Budi 8.2 (ADR-0089).
// Budi is no longer in your network path — your agent talks directly to the
// LLM provider, and the daemon tails the transcript files the agent already
// writes locally. Inlined for zero JS, minimal request count, and good
// print/dark-mode contrast.
---

<figure
  class="card overflow-hidden p-4 sm:p-6"
  aria-label="Diagram: your AI agent talks directly to the LLM provider. The agent writes a transcript file to disk on your machine. A small Rust daemon tails that transcript locally. An optional, opt-in dotted arrow sends pre-aggregated daily numbers to app.getbudi.dev."
>
  <svg
    role="img"
    aria-hidden="true"
    viewBox="0 0 720 280"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    class="h-auto w-full"
  >
    <defs>
      <marker
        id="arrowhead"
        markerWidth="10"
        markerHeight="10"
        refX="8"
        refY="5"
        orient="auto"
        markerUnits="strokeWidth"
      >
        <path d="M0,0 L0,10 L10,5 z" fill="currentColor"></path>
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <g
      font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace"
      font-size="13"
      fill="#e6e8ec"
    >
      {/* Agent (top-left) */}
      <g>
        <rect x="20" y="30" width="180" height="90" rx="12" fill="#11141a" stroke="#313846"></rect>
        <text x="110" y="62" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="600">your agent</text>
        <text x="110" y="84" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >claude · cursor</text
        >
        <text x="110" y="100" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >codex · copilot</text
        >
      </g>

      {/* LLM provider (top-right) — direct, Budi is NOT in this path */}
      <g>
        <rect x="520" y="30" width="180" height="90" rx="12" fill="#11141a" stroke="#313846"></rect>
        <text x="610" y="62" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="600"
          >LLM provider</text
        >
        <text x="610" y="84" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >anthropic · openai</text
        >
        <text x="610" y="100" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11">github</text>
      </g>

      {/* Direct arrow agent → provider (no Budi in the middle) */}
      <g stroke="#9aa3b2" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" color="#9aa3b2">
        <line x1="200" y1="75" x2="518" y2="75" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></line>
      </g>
      <text x="360" y="60" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11">
        direct — Budi is not in the network path
      </text>

      {/* Transcript on disk (bottom-left under agent) */}
      <g>
        <rect x="20" y="160" width="180" height="80" rx="10" fill="#11141a" stroke="#313846"></rect>
        <text x="110" y="190" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="600"
          >transcript on disk</text
        >
        <text x="110" y="210" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >~/.claude/projects</text
        >
        <text x="110" y="226" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >~/.codex/sessions · …</text
        >
      </g>

      {/* Agent writes transcript */}
      <g stroke="#9aa3b2" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" color="#9aa3b2">
        <line x1="110" y1="120" x2="110" y2="158" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></line>
      </g>

      {/* Budi daemon (bottom-middle) */}
      <g>
        <rect x="265" y="155" width="190" height="95" rx="14" fill="#0f1f17" stroke="#22c55e"
        ></rect>
        <text x="360" y="185" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="#22c55e"
          >budi-daemon</text
        >
        <text x="360" y="207" text-anchor="middle" fill="#cbd5e1" font-size="11">tails JSONL</text>
        <text x="360" y="223" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >~6 MB Rust · port 7878</text
        >
        <text x="360" y="239" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >on your machine</text
        >
      </g>

      {/* Tail arrow: transcript → daemon */}
      <g stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" color="#22c55e">
        <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="262" y2="200" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></line>
      </g>

      {/* Optional cloud arrow (daemon → cloud), bottom-right */}
      <g stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-dasharray="5 5" fill="none" color="#22c55e">
        <path d="M 455 215 C 540 215, 600 215, 620 215" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></path>
      </g>
      <text x="540" y="245" text-anchor="middle" fill="#22c55e" font-size="11">
        opt-in: aggregates only
      </text>
      <text x="540" y="259" text-anchor="middle" fill="#22c55e" font-size="11">
        → app.getbudi.dev
      </text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="sr-only">
    Your agent talks directly to the upstream LLM provider — Budi is not in the network path. The
    agent writes a transcript JSONL file to disk locally (for example, to ~/.claude/projects or
    ~/.codex/sessions). The budi-daemon process tails that transcript on your machine on port 7878.
    Optionally, the daemon can sync only pre-aggregated daily numbers to app.getbudi.dev.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
